title: [LucarioPK-Animelee Subs] Pocket Monsters Best Wishes Decolora A
description:
Hello, LucarioPK of LucarioPK Subs here. You might remember me from Detective Conan subs. I took off with episode 687 of that series, and we're still going strong. 

Anyways, this is supposed to serve as a teaser of what's to come next. My brother and I are known amongst the Pokemon community, and it's time we gave back. 

Introducing, LucarioPK-Animelee Subs!

Every Thursday afternoon, we're going to make it our priority to sub each brand new episode of Pocket Monsters ASAP! 

You can find out more about LucarioPK Subs here, and watch out for updates on the social media and website!

Website will be up and running next week!
